"30090005001-00", "V1.2 A31", and an anti-static warning logo is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
This FCC ID also covers the FWR-714N (w/ external antennas).
A label with a MAC having a 34:BD:F9 OUI is affixed to the back of the board in the FCC photos. The FCC manual shows the device with a 00:0C:43 OUI (and a sample SSID of '''feixun-XXXXXX''' [last 6 digits of wireless MAC]).
